History.Citadel of Assassins:
Instead, Athrogate became a supreme killer, an agent of the [[Tightpurse]] thieves guild of [[Heliogabalus]] and associated with the [[Citadel of Assassins]]. Thus, during his time in Damara, he was often accompanied by [[Canthan Doolittle]], a wizard of the Citadel of Assassins.

In the {{YearlinkName|1368}}, Athrogate became a member of a group of warriors chosen by Commander [[Ellery Dragonsbane]] to fight the legacy of [[Zhengyi]], the Witch-King. This group included [[Artemis Entreri]] and [[Jarlaxle]]. Athrogate was subsequently arrested by the [[monk]] Grandmaster [[Kane]] and held in prison for a long time. He was freed when Entreri, now styling himself King Artemis the First, was captured by the [[paladin]] King [[Gareth Dragonsbane]] and Jarlaxle saved them.

